TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {23443=2011: Started all 10 games at slotback, totaling a conference-best 1,561 all-purpose yards and 12 touchdowns ... rushed 128 times for 867 yards and nine touchdowns and caught 25 passes for 378 yards and two more scores ... also returned 13 kickoffs for a 24.3 yard average and another touchdown ... received First Team All-ODAC, First Team All-State and First Team All-South Region accolades ... also named the 2011 ODAC Scholar-Athlete of the Year and Capital One Second Team Academic All-American ... totaled a season-best 236 all-purpose yards and one touchdown in a 34-30 win over Randolph-Macon (10/15) ... rushed for a career-best 200 yards and two touchdowns on just 15 carries in a 49-42 win over Alma (9/24) ... tallied 199 all-purpose yards (137 rushing) and scored a touchdown in a 42-35 loss to Centre (9/17) ... registered 197 all-purpose yards (123 rushing) and totaled three touchdowns in a 52-42 win over Bridgewater (10/22) ... recorded an 82-yard kickoff return for a touchdown in a 49-13 win over Catholic (10/28).}
